Package ch.njol.util

Class Math2

java.lang.Object
ch.njol.util.Math2
@Internal public final class Math2 extends Object
This class is not to be used by addons. In the future methods may change signature, contract and/or get removed without warning.

Behaviour for an edge case like NaN or infinite is undefined.
